juga ditinggalkan.

58
00:03:38,250 --> 00:03:39,380
Memang aneh.

59
00:03:40,510 --> 00:03:41,150
Kak San.

60
00:03:41,150 --> 00:03:42,080
Aku pergi lihat.

61
00:03:45,350 --> 00:03:46,450
Jaga keselamatan.

62
00:04:27,210 --> 00:04:30,310
Sepanjang jalan ada lampu,
tapi tak ada suara sedikit pun.

63
00:04:41,350 --> 00:04:42,550
Tolong.

64
00:04:42,810 --> 00:04:43,910
Tolong!

65
00:04:43,910 --> 00:04:45,450
Ada apa? Apa yang terjadi?

66
