Jangan takut,
aku akan lindungi kalian.

67
00:04:57,550 --> 00:04:58,210
Hentikan!

68
00:05:06,150 --> 00:05:07,010
Xiangxiang!

69
00:05:11,210 --> 00:05:11,810
Rongrong.

70
00:05:11,810 --> 00:05:12,350
Zhuqing.

71
00:05:12,350 --> 00:05:13,080
Kalian tinggal.

72
00:05:13,250 --> 00:05:14,480
Bantu aku jaga Xiao Wu.

73
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:14,980
Baiklah.

74
00:05:16,550 --> 00:05:18,417
Teknik pertama
Piramida Lautan Dunia,…

75
00:05:18,417 --> 00:05:20,180
…Perlindungan Lautan Dunia.

76
00:05:23,510 --> 00:05:25,150
Oscar, kau lindungi mereka.

77
00:05:25,550 --> 00:05:26,280
Hati-hati.

78
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:27,180
Kak Dai.

79
00:05:27,180 --> 00:05:27,950
Ayo pergi.

80
00:06:00,510 --> 00:06:01,210
Bandit Serigala.

81
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:04,210
Tak sangka di Kekaisaran Tiandou
juga ada Bandit Serigala.

82
00:06:04,480 --> 00:06:05,450
Bandit Serigala?

83
00:06:05,750 --> 00:06:06,710
Mereka manusia?

84
00:06:06,710 --> 00:06:09,550
Gabungan manusia dan Monster Roh
Serigala Badai Iblis.

85
00:06:09,550 --> 00:06:11,250
Monster setengah manusia
dan serigala.

86
00:06:11,250 --> 00:06:13,550
Roh Pelindung Serigala Ganda Badai
milik Feng Xiaotian,…

87
00:06:13,550 --> 00:06:15,650
…adalah fisik kuat mutasi
dari Serigala Badai Iblis.

88
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:19,717
Jadi, Bandit Serigala punya
fisik dan kekuatan…

89
00:06:19,717 --> 00:06:20,880
…bagai Serigala Badai Iblis…

90
00:06:21,350 --> 00:06:23,150
…dan punya kecerdasan
seperti manusia.

91
00:06:23,650 --> 00:06:24,380
Benar.

92
00:06:24,980 --> 00:06:26,410
Mereka menyukai darah,…

93
00:06:26,650 --> 00:06:28,480
…suka menyerang manusia
sebagai makanan.

94
00:06:28,980 --> 00:06:30,650
Begitu menyerang,
maka tak akan berhenti.

95
00:06:30,880 --> 00:06:31,850
Sangat sulit dihadapi.

96
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:33,110
Lima ratus Bandit Serigala…

97
00:06:33,110 --> 00:06:35,110
…bisa kalahkan puluhan ribu
prajurit terlatih.

98
00:06:36,300 --> 00:06:39,050
Kita sulit hadapi begitu banyak
Bandit Serigala secara langsung.

99
00:06:39,050 --> 00:06:39,750
Bagaimana?

100
00:06:49,780 --> 00:06:50,350
Hentikan!

101
00:07:01,880 --> 00:07:03,810
Lawan kalian ada di sini.

102
00:07:19,450 --> 00:07:21,880
Teknik roh ke-4,
Meteor Harimau Putih!

103
00:07:27,350 --> 00:07:28,410
Kak San.

104
00:07:28,880 --> 00:07:29,580
Xiangxiang.

105
00:07:29,950 --> 00:07:30,850
Kau tak terluka, 'kan?

106
00:07:32,880 --> 00:07:33,780
Aku baik-baik saja.

107
00:08:10,650 --> 00:08:11,410
Xiangxiang.

108
00:08:11,410 --> 00:08:12,680
Kau bawa penduduk untuk kabur.

109
00:08:12,680 --> 00:08:13,980
Serahkan tempat ini pada kami.

110
00:08:14,780 --> 00:08:15,950
Semuanya ikut aku.

111
00:08:24,750 --> 00:08:26,210
Bandit Serigala ini hanya bawahan.

112
00:08:26,680 --> 00:08:29,150
Di kelompok mereka
pasti ada pemimpin.

113
00:08:29,580 --> 00:08:30,910
Asalkan menangkap pemimpinnya,…

114
00:08:31,050 --> 00:08:33,350
…Bandit Serigala yang tersisa
akan kacau sendiri.

115
00:08:39,450 --> 00:08:41,010
Pemimpin Bandit Serigala
tak di sini.

116
00:08:52,550 --> 00:08:54,450
Aku harus mempercayai mereka.

117
00:09:17,950 --> 00:09:19,150
Kak Dai, hati-hati!

118
00:09:28,580 --> 00:09:29,380
Gendut.

119
00:09:29,380 --> 00:09:30,310
Serang dari udara.

120
00:09:30,310 --> 00:09:30,950
Baik.

121
00:09:31,750 --> 00:09:32,980
Teknik roh pertama.

122
00:09:32,980 --> 00:09:33,950
Tembakan Api Phoenix.

123
00:09:44,350 --> 00:09:45,310
Sial.

124
00:09:47,650 --> 00:09:48,980
Sungguh tak ada habisnya.

125
00:09:52,530 --> 00:09:53,500
Sudah dikepung.

126
00:09:53,500 --> 00:09:54,440
Bagaimana ini, Xiao San?

127
00:10:14,780 --> 00:10:23,680
=Dunia Roh=

128
00:10:49,910 --> 00:10:50,680
Kalian pergi dulu.

129
00:10:50,680 --> 00:10:51,750
Aku tahan mereka.

130
00:11:35,710 --> 00:11:37,510
Masih tak berhenti?

131
00:11:53,650 --> 00:11:54,450
Xiangxiang!

132
00:11:57,450 --> 00:11:58,550
Sial.

