135
00:12:04,180 --> 00:12:04,980
Tidak bisa.

136
00:12:04,980 --> 00:12:06,410
Xiangxiang masih di tangan mereka.

137
00:12:07,710 --> 00:12:12,680
Jika ingin wanita ini hidup,
gantikan dengan nyawa kalian.

138
00:12:12,680 --> 00:12:13,480
Jangan!

139
00:12:14,580 --> 00:12:15,480
Xiao San.

140
00:12:15,480 --> 00:12:16,450
Bagaimana ini?

141
00:12:29,950 --> 00:12:32,380
Kami setujui persyaratanmu.

142
00:12:34,250 --> 00:12:34,950
Tidak!

143
00:12:37,710 --> 00:12:38,380
Gendut.

144
00:12:38,950 --> 00:12:40,980
Kuserahkan Xiangxiang padamu.

145
00:12:53,210 --> 00:12:57,180
Teknik Kelinci Tulang Lunak.
Perisai Emas Tak Tertembus.

146
00:13:01,150 --> 00:13:02,380
Lakukan sesuai rencana.

147
00:13:02,380 --> 00:13:03,180
Apa?

148
00:13:03,380 --> 00:13:04,720
Serangan Kematian Harimau Putih.

149
00:13:06,150 --> 00:13:07,550
Cahaya Ungu Dewa.

150
00:14:04,050 --> 00:14:04,910
Xiangxiang.

151
00:14:05,310 --> 00:14:07,650
