154
00:14:22,010 --> 00:14:22,950
Kondisi liar.

155
00:14:25,880 --> 00:14:26,580
Bagaimana ini?

156
00:14:26,580 --> 00:14:27,280
Biar aku saja.

157
00:14:27,450 --> 00:14:28,480
Kalian cepat mundur.

158
00:15:04,110 --> 00:15:06,250
Hilang semua dalam sekejap.

159
00:15:06,250 --> 00:15:08,250
Kak San, kau sungguh sangat hebat.

160
00:15:08,250 --> 00:15:08,780
Xiao San.

161
00:15:09,150 --> 00:15:10,550
Sebenarnya kau pakai jurus apa?

162
00:15:18,350 --> 00:15:19,310
Kak San.

163
