butuh Tulang Roh.

170
00:15:40,650 --> 00:15:41,450
Kakak Dai.

171
00:15:41,450 --> 00:15:42,350
Jangan sungkan lagi.

172
00:15:42,550 --> 00:15:44,010
Jika aku tak salah tebak,…

173
00:15:44,010 --> 00:15:46,480
