sangat mungkin adalah Pengamuk.

174
00:15:46,480 --> 00:15:47,950
Sangat berguna bagimu.

175
00:15:58,450 --> 00:15:59,550
Kak San.

176
00:15:59,550 --> 00:16:01,550
Lihat bagaimana keadaan penduduk.

177
00:16:01,550 --> 00:16:02,510
Aku temani kamu.

178
00:16:02,980 --> 00:16:03,780
Pergilah.

179
00:16:03,780 --> 00:16:04,580
Di sini ada aku.

180
00:16:18,050 --> 00:16:18,650
Sebelah sini.

181
00:16:30,750 --> 00:16:31,950
Apa yang kau lakukan?

182
00:17:22,280 --> 00:17:24,180
Cepat datang bantu.

183
00:17:24,480 --> 00:17:25,210
Aku datang.

184
00:17:31,710 --> 00:17:32,550
Xiangxiang.

185
00:17:32,810 --> 00:17:34,380
